0x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a>分享了她“奇怪”的第二张专辑的最新动态——看看她在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467">Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/chappell-roan-good-luck-babe-fame-fans-1235094314/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em>的新专题</a>中，这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>对《中西部公主的兴衰》的后续作品如何进行了新的阐述。这张专辑仍在制作中，没有任何关于何时发布的暗示，但查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 现在透露，她已经为该项目完成了大约五六首歌曲。</p><p> “我们有一首乡村歌曲。我们有一首舞曲。我们有一种真正的八十年代风格，我们有一种原声音乐，还有一种真正有机的、现场乐队的、七十年代的氛围。这太奇怪了，”她告诉<em>滚石杂志</em>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3582586" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3582586" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3582586" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270.jpg" alt="NME 2024 年封面 CHAPPELL ROAN 摄影：KRISTEN JAN WONG" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/NME-THE-COVER-2024-CHAPPELL-ROAN-COVER-CREDIT-KRISTEN-JAN-WONG-PLAYLIST-HERO@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3582586" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：NME 的 Kristen Jan Wong</figcaption></figure><p>她还谈到了“The Subway”，这是一首她整个夏天都在现场表演的未发行歌曲。然而，她并不认为这首歌会成为她的下一首单曲：“我只是喜欢表演它。我还有另外两首我也很想表演，但我不知道接下来会发生什么。当我不知道时，它只是还没有击中我，因为通常我知道。我总有一个答案。我不认为这是“地铁”。 ”</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><em>《NME》</em>封面明星</a>去年九月发行了她的首张录音室专辑“The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess”，广受好评。 <i>《NME》</i>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/lollapalooza">四星评论</a>中将其描述为“罗恩大胆而厚颜无耻的笔的展示，她在其中将灼热的启示与一些可爱的厚颜无耻的合唱一起放置”。</p><p>从那时起，她的第一张专辑在发行近一年后就获得了英国冠军—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-congratulates-chappell-roan-on-chart-success-the-meteoric-rise-of-a-midwestern-princess-3782611">埃尔顿·约翰最近对此表示祝贺</a>。罗恩分享了单曲“祝你好运，宝贝！”今年四月。这首歌在英国排名第四，并于六月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-sabrina-carpenters-stripped-back-cover-of-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-for-bbc-radio-one-live-lounge-3766709">在 BBC Live Lounge 被 Sabrina Carpenter 翻唱</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3789250" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789250" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789250" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan.jpg" alt="查普尔·罗恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789250" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 将于 2024 年 8 月 20 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 Intuit Dome 举行的奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) “GUTS”世界巡演中进行表演。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Billboard via Getty Images </figcaption></figure><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-cancels-scalper-tickets-to-sell-to-actual-fans-3790775"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>罗恩最近还公开反对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">粉丝的“奇怪”和“令人毛骨悚然”的行为，告诉他们：“这不正常。”</a>她的言论赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Paramore">帕拉莫尔</a>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/Hayley-Williams">海莉·威廉姆斯</a>的赞扬，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-supports-chappell-roans-brave-and-unfortunately-necessary-boundary-comments-3787404">在 Instagram 上称赞这位流行歌星“勇敢”</a> 。</p><p>从那时起，她最近表示，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">Hayley Williams</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">Katy Perry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">MUNA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">Lorde</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">boygenius</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mitski">Mitski</a>在内的众多艺术家都全力支持这一主题。 。 </p></div></div><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mitski-welcomed-chappell-roan-to-the-shittiest-exclusive-club-in-the-world-and-warned-of-fandom-3792427"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-fans-react-after-she-posts-vma-rehearsal-photos-ahead-of-cancelled-gigs-3790886">罗恩在因“日程冲突”而取消两场即将举行的欧洲演出之前，分享了一张VMA排练照片，引发了粉丝们的分歧</a>。在其他地方，粉丝们对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kacey-musgraves-cover-chappell-roans-pink-pony-club-3791155">Kacey Musgraves 翻唱的 2020 年歌曲《Pink Pony Club》</a>反应热烈。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-shares-update-on-weird-new-album-3792501">Chappell Roan 分享有关“怪异”新专辑的更新的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
坏兔子加入亚当桑德勒的《快乐吉尔摩2》演员阵容https://www.nme.com/news/film/bad-bunny-joins-adam-sandler-happy-gilmore-2-3792474?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bad-bunny-joins-adam-sandler-happy-吉尔莫-2Chris Edwards Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:02:14 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsNetflixRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3792474 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>续集已正式开始制作</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bad-bunny-joins-adam-sandler-happy-gilmore-2-3792474">《坏兔子》加入亚当·桑德勒的《快乐吉尔摩 2》演员阵容</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Bad-Bunny-and-Adam-Sandler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">坏兔子</a>（真名贝尼托·安东尼奥·马丁内斯·奥卡西奥）已与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adam-sandler">亚当·桑德勒</a>一起出演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/happy-gilmore-2-is-officially-happening-next-month-3785675"><em>《快乐吉尔摩 2》</em></a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/adam-sandlers-happy-gilmore-is-getting-a-sequel-3756785">流媒体服务公司于 5 月证实了 1996 年高尔夫喜剧续集的</a>消息，该公司将监督该电影的制作。</p><p>续集的剧情细节（本月正式开始制作）目前仍处于保密状态，因此<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/bad-bunny-adam-sandler-happy-gilmore-sequel-netflix-1235996106/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">目前还不清楚说唱歌手将扮演谁</a>。朱莉·鲍文和克里斯托弗·麦克唐纳将继续出演原著中的角色，而凯尔·纽瓦切克（ <em>《谋杀之谜</em>》）将担任导演。</p><p>周二（8 月 20 日），桑德勒在<i>出席《吉米·法伦今夜秀》</i>节目时表示，这部电影将于今年 9 月开始拍摄。</p><p> “很好。我们为剧本付出了很多努力。我们不想让任何人失望。我们想出了一个主意——我们就放弃了，”他说。请观看下面的完整采访。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="亚当·桑德勒 (Adam Sandler) 畅谈《快乐吉尔摩 2》、特拉维斯·凯尔斯 (Travis Kelce) 客串和纽约地铁街头表演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FfpcbbRuirQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，桑德勒透露，美国国家橄榄球联盟 (NFL) 球星兼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>(Taylor Swift) 的男友特拉维斯·凯尔斯 (Travis Kelce) 将在这部电影中露面。 “好大一个帅哥啊。有趣又酷，”桑德勒说。 “他是个种马，而且很有趣。”</p><p>在原版电影中，桑德勒饰演哈皮·吉尔摩（Happy Gilmore），他是一名患有愤怒管理问题的曲棍球运动员，但发现自己也擅长高尔夫。</p><p>吉尔摩参加了一场高尔夫锦标赛，以赢得金钱来拯救祖母的房子，一路上与傲慢的射手麦加文（麦当劳饰）对峙。这部电影还由已故的卡尔·韦瑟斯和鲍勃·巴克主演。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">快乐的吉尔摩回来了！亚当·桑德勒将在 Netflix 推出的一部全新电影中再次扮演他的标志性角色。 <a href="https://t.co/AERdtqlJ6j">pic.twitter.com/AERdtqlJ6j</a></p><p> - Netflix (@netflix) <a href="http