ync" class="size-full wp-image-3792455" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram.jpg" alt="Zone 的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图。图片来源：Zone / Instagram" width="1500" height="2678" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram-400x714.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram-800x1428.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram-696x1243.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram-1392x2485.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screengrab-of-Zhones-Instagram-Story.-Credit-Zhone-_Instagram-1068x1907.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792455" class="wp-caption-text"> Zone 的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图。图片来源：Zone / Instagram</figcaption></figure><p>如果这篇神秘的帖子确实是 Sivan 和 Lipa 的混音版，那么它将会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-troye-sivan-announce-charli-xcx-troye-sivan-present-sweat-north-american-arena-tour-3619000">Charli XCX 和 Troye Sivan 准备在本月晚些时候开始他们的“Sweat”巡演</a>时发布。</p><p>演出将于周六（9 月 14 日）开始，并在底特律小凯撒体育场 (Little Caesars Arena) 举行开幕演出。从那里出发，它将在波士顿、纽约、多伦多、菲尼克斯、洛杉矶等地停靠，然后于 10 月 23 日在西雅图结束。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/charli-xcx-tickets/artist/1638380?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=VpWUfT1MIxyKUdezP0T4MUL-UkC3gvRk2VqI2k0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取剩余门票。<